<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>All about me.</h1>

      <hr>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">

          <%= image_tag "pineapple.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        </div>

        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>My name is Brian Anderson, and I'm excited to begin my Development career! Coding has been quite the adventure so far and I can't wait to see where it takes me.</p>

          <p>I've been married for a little over a year. In the winter, snowboarding is a really big part of my life. I also really like to watch and play basketball.</p>
        

        <p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" 
                  type="button" 
                  data-toggle="collapse" 
                  data-target="#jobHistory"
                  aria-expanded="false" 
                  aria-controller="jobHistory">Job History</button>

          <button class="btn btn-primary" 
                  type="button" 
                  data-toggle="collapse" 
                  data-target="#education"
                  aria-expanded="false" 
                  aria-controller="education">Education</button>

                  <button class="btn btn-primary" 
                  type="button" 
                  data-toggle="collapse" 
                  data-target="#skills"
                  aria-expanded="false" 
                  aria-controller="education">Skills</button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Vivint - 5 Months
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Vantage Marketing - 3 Months
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Blendtec - 4 Years
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Snow College
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Southern Utah University
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="skills">
            <div class="card card-block">
             <div class="skills">
              <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                <div class="skill">
                  <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                  <div class="progress">
                    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                         role="progressbar"
                         aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                         aria-valuemax="100"
                         style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                    ></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




